    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Project Description</h3>
      <p>
        This prototype was designed to increase engagement in a younger audience at the National Art Gallery of Canada by gamifying the experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        The app would lead players in a scavenger hunt by providing them with small sections of a painting within the gallery, which they would then have to find in the physical world.
      </p>
      <p>
        3 modes allow the player to play alone, competitively against their opponents, or cooperatively with their teammates. 
      </p>
      <h3>Project Team</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Armine Hollohan</strong>: 2D Artist</li>
